Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.99,0:00:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要知道了方法就很简单了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.96,0:00:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话我就不会输了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.69,0:00:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.89,0:00:46.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是冲着这东西来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.19,0:00:52.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想欠你人情  这样就两清了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.32,0:00:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.99,0:00:55.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回去吧  小圆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.41,0:00:58.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙耶香…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.13,0:01:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微有点累了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.05,0:01:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要勉强  抓着我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.31,0:01:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个笨蛋
